text: Negrea may refer to: * Negrea, a village in Hîncești District, Moldova * Negrea, a village in the commune Schela, Galați County, Romania * Negrea, a tributary of the Crișul Repede in Cluj County, Romania * Negrea (Lozova), a tributary of the Lozova in Galați County, Romania * Negrea (beetle), a genus of beetles == See also == * Neagra (disambiguation) * Neagra River (disambiguation)
title: Negrea (disambiguation)
